  "text": "Exposure and all soccer injuries were recorded during the 2009-2010 competitive season, from the first competition match until the last regular competition match of the season. Table 1 shows the used definitions. These are in accordance with the consensus statement by Fuller et al. [CITATION_1] In addition, team and player compliance was recorded by all coaches in the intervention group using the exposure form.",
